name: imgNotes
tagline: Extension of the jQuery imgViewer plugin to add markers and notes to the image
body:
imgNotes is an extension of the jQuery [imgViewer](https://github.com/waynegm/imgViewer) plugin that adds markers and notes to an image that can be zoomed in and out with the mousewheel and panned around by click and drag.
